MouseClick.Script:
(A:GPS drives NAV1, bool) if{ quit }
(L:CDI source selected, enum) 1 == 
if{
	(A:NAV1 radial, degrees) 180 - dnor
	(>K:VOR1_SET) 
} 
(L:CDI source selected, enum) 2 == 
if{
	(A:NAV2 radial, degrees) 180 - dnor
	(>K:VOR2_SET) 
}
(P:Absolute time, seconds) (>L:time crs changed, seconds)

